www.nme.com/artists/yasiin-bey">Yasiin Bey</a> 。</p><p> Artists for Aid 演出将于 7 月 4 日星期四在伦敦 Troxy 举行。这场演出是与<a href="http://www.warchild.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国战争儿童组织 (War Child UK)</a>合作的，继今年年初<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stormzy-and-clairo-lead-artists-for-aid-concert-for-gaza-and-sudan-line-up-3561172">在新泽西州举办了第一届演出</a>之后。 <a href="https://dice.fm/partner/dice/event/avvlm2-artists-for-aid-4th-jul-troxy-london-tickets?dice_id=3455781&amp;dice_channel=web&amp;dice_tags=organic&amp;dice_campaign=DICE&amp;dice_feature=mio_marketing&amp;_branch_match_id=1318912779492293571&amp;_branch_referrer=H4sIAAAAAAAAA8soKSkottLXz8nMy9ZLyUxO1UvL1S9KNLUwN0oyTE21SAQA%2BXAJDyEAAAA%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>购买门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3769308" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3769308" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3769308" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="穆斯塔法的伦敦援助艺术家海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Mustafas-Artists-for-Aid-London-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3769308" class="wp-caption-text">穆斯塔法的伦敦援助艺术家海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>“伦敦！苏丹在打来电话。加沙在召唤。这里的每一位艺术家都是同理心的英雄，感谢你们响应我们的号召。门票今天下午 5 点在 artsforaid.org 发售。这是一场战争，引起共鸣，呼喊答案，”穆斯塔法在 Instagram 上宣布演出的帖子的标题写道。</p><p>第一届艺术家援助慈善演出吸引了 Clairo、Stormzy、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/omar-apollo">Omar Apollo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/6lack">6lack</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/070-shake">070 Shake</a> 、Charlotte Day Wilson、Mohammed El Kurd、Nick Hakim 等人的表演。</p><p>穆斯塔法在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0-j1kBL57t/?img_index=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>帖子中写道：“我们不知疲倦地努力把这首歌带给你们，但我们的疲劳甚至不足以影响我们歌唱的目的。在过去的几年里，我访问了我的祖国苏丹和巴勒斯坦。</p><p> “我访问这两个地方的主要目的是与艺术家社区、年轻的组织者建立联系——寻找悲伤、希望和信仰的相似之处。两国的暴力夺走了这个梦想。在这里，它以某种方式为我复活了。我们的意图依然存在，今晚我们发出自己的声音，为他们的声音腾出空间。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0-j1kBL57t/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlin