>Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip</a> 。还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-rumours-spread-of-secret-coldplay-show-at-local-venue-3769280">传言称附近有酷玩乐队的秘密演出</a>。</p><p>本月初，组织者透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">门票全部售完的狂欢节的完整阵容、舞台划分和时间安排</a>——包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-react-as-full-glastonbury-2024-line-up-and-schedule-reveals-new-names-and-clashes-3762343">一些新名字</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/who-will-play-the-big-glastonbury-tba-secret-sets-fans-are-guessing-3762542">各种“TBA”秘密时段</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bbc">BBC</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bbc-announces-glastonbury-2024-coverage-plans-3760796">分享了其对音乐周末的广泛报道计划</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3769283" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3769283" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3769283" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Michael-Eavis-2024@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节第二天，格拉斯顿伯里音乐节创始人 Michael Eavis 出现在公园舞台上" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Michael-Eavis-2024@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Michael-Eavis-2024@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Michael-Eavis-2024@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Michael-Eavis-2024@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Michael-Eavis-2024@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Michael-Eavis-2024@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1